23#define MPFR_NEED_LONGLONG_H
24#include "mpfr-impl.h"
25
26#ifndef MPFR_USE_MINI_GMP
27/*
28 * Set f to z, choosing the smallest precision for f
29 * so that z = f*(2^BPML)*zs*2^(RetVal)
30 */
31static int
32set_z (mpfr_ptr f, mpz_srcptr z, mp_size_t *zs)
33{
34 mp_limb_t *p;
35 mp_size_t s;
36 int c;
37 mpfr_prec_t pf;
38
39 MPFR_ASSERTD (mpz_sgn (z) != 0);
40
41 /* Remove useless ending 0 */
42 for (p = PTR (z), s = *zs = ABSIZ (z) ; *p == 0; p++, s--)
43 MPFR_ASSERTD (s >= 0);
44
45 /* Get working precision */
46 count_leading_zeros (c, p[s-1]);
47 pf = s * GMP_NUMB_BITS - c;
48 if (pf < MPFR_PREC_MIN)
49 pf = MPFR_PREC_MIN;
50 mpfr_init2 (f, pf);
51
52 /* Copy Mantissa */
53 if (MPFR_LIKELY (c))
54 mpn_lshift (MPFR_MANT (f), p, s, c);
55 else
56 MPN_COPY (MPFR_MANT (f), p, s);
57
58 MPFR_SET_SIGN (f, mpz_sgn (z));
59 MPFR_SET_EXP (f, 0);
60
61 return -c;
62}
63
64/* set f to the rational q */
65int
66mpfr_set_q (mpfr_ptr f, mpq_srcptr q, mpfr_rnd_t rnd)
67{
68 mpz_srcptr num, den;
69 mpfr_t n, d;
70 int inexact;
71 int cn, cd;
72 long shift;
73 mp_size_t sn, sd;
74 MPFR_SAVE_EXPO_DECL (expo);
75
76 num = mpq_numref (q);
77 den = mpq_denref (q);
78 /* NAN and INF for mpq are not really documented, but could be found */
79 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY (mpz_sgn (num) == 0))
80 {
81 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY (mpz_sgn (den) == 0))
82 {
83 MPFR_SET_NAN (f);
84 MPFR_RET_NAN;
85 }
86 else
87 {
88 MPFR_SET_ZERO (f);
89 MPFR_SET_POS (f);
90 MPFR_RET (0);
91 }
92 }
93 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY (mpz_sgn (den) == 0))
94 {
95 MPFR_SET_INF (f);
96 MPFR_SET_SIGN (f, mpz_sgn (num));
97 MPFR_RET (0);
98 }
99
100 MPFR_SAVE_EXPO_MARK (expo);
101
102 cn = set_z (n, num, &sn);
103 cd = set_z (d, den, &sd);
104
105 sn -= sd;
106 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY (sn > MPFR_EMAX_MAX / GMP_NUMB_BITS))
107 {
108 MPFR_SAVE_EXPO_FREE (expo);
109 inexact = mpfr_overflow (f, rnd, MPFR_SIGN (f));
110 goto end;
111 }
112 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY (sn < MPFR_EMIN_MIN / GMP_NUMB_BITS -1))
113 {
114 MPFR_SAVE_EXPO_FREE (expo);
115 if (rnd == MPFR_RNDN)
116 rnd = MPFR_RNDZ;
117 inexact = mpfr_underflow (f, rnd, MPFR_SIGN (f));
118 goto end;
119 }
120
121 inexact = mpfr_div (f, n, d, rnd);
122 shift = GMP_NUMB_BITS*sn+cn-cd;
123 MPFR_ASSERTD (shift == GMP_NUMB_BITS*sn+cn-cd);
124 cd = mpfr_mul_2si (f, f, shift, rnd);
125 MPFR_SAVE_EXPO_FREE (expo);
126 if (MPFR_UNLIKELY (cd != 0))
127 inexact = cd;
128 else
129 inexact = mpfr_check_range (f, inexact, rnd);
130 end:
131 mpfr_clear (d);
132 mpfr_clear (n);
133 MPFR_RET (inexact);
134}
135#endif
